# 🌐 YourName.github.io

Personal website and portfolio built using **HTML + CSS**, hosted free on **GitHub Pages**.

### 🔗 Live site
👉 [https://yourusername.github.io](https://yourusername.github.io)

### 🧩 Features
- Minimal, responsive single-page layout  
- Easy to customize text, colors, and links  
- No ads, no frameworks required  

### 🛠️ How to update
1. Edit `index.html` directly in GitHub or push updates via Git.  
2. Commit your changes — GitHub Pages redeploys automatically.  

